The {{server.xml}} as part of the confluence distribution has an explicit reference to and old version of the Coyote Connector.

{quote}
<Connector className="org.apache.coyote.tomcat4.CoyoteConnector" ... >
{quote}

There is no reference to the {{className}} attribute in the [tomcat 5 reference|http://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-5.5-doc/config/http.html] so its possible that its not being used.

We should remove the attribute.

